<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab>Lieber Wysentawer, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt <app>
<note place="interlinear">b </note>
</app> Conrad <expan>Paumgartn<ex>er</ex></expan> der
                            <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex></expan>, <app>
<note place="interlinear">a </note>
</app> Hans Groland, <add>des <expan cert="unknwon">S.</expan> sun</add>,
                        Craft Kresse <app>
<note place="interlinear"> b </note>
</app> und Dyetrich Dorner, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wie ir ir armleute von Massendorff <add>zu
                            Spalt</add> bekümert und verpoten habt und maint, die vogtber <expan>cze
                                mach<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das doch vormals nye gewesen sey,
                                <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> fleissiklich, daz ir der
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> armleute ledig und unbekümert lassen wöllet
                        und sie dabey lasset <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als sie von
                        alterherkumen sein. Das wollen etc. Und het <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan> czu <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iren
                                <expan>arme<ex>n</ex>leute<ex>n</ex></expan> icht
                                <expan>czusprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, darümb wir ir yeder von
                                <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogens</expan> slewnigs rehten beholffen sein,
                                <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> er des <expan>erma<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
                        wirdt. Und lat uns des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> freuntlich
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> wissen bey dem
                            <expan>gegenwertige<ex>n</ex></expan>, der ew disen
                                <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in vigilia
                                <expan>purificac<ex>ionis</ex></expan>
<expan>Ma<ex>r</ex>ie.</expan>
</ab></div>
